data.description: Nestled in the picturesque landscape of Vail, Arizona, this 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home is a desert gem.  Upon arrival, you'll be charmed by the inviting curb appeal and well-kept desert landscaping. Inside, an open-concept living area welcomes you with abundant natural light. The master bedroom is a haven of peace, featuring a roomy layout, walk-in closet, and an en-suite bathroom with a soaking tub, and a separate shower. Two additional bedrooms offer flexibility for guests or a home office, with 2 bathrooms ensuring convenience for all. Additional amenities include a 2-car garage, a laundry room, and ample storage solutions throughout.If you're seeking a home that embraces the tranquility of the desert while offering modern comfort and style, this home is your answer.
